(54, 'Follow UP: Implementation and NOC Cross Departmental meeting', '2016-07-20 11:30:00', 'anika.sharmin@summitcommunications.net,razib.hasan@summitcommunications.net,ehsan.karim@summitcommunications.net,ibrahim.sharif@summitcommunications.net,ishtiak.mahmud@summitcommunications.net,minhazul.islam@summitcommunications.net,fahim.shahariar@summitcommunications.net,saeed.naser@summitcommunications.net', 'anika.sharmin@summitcommunications.net,razib.hasan@summitcommunications.net,mir.raihan@summitcommunications.net,ehsan.karim@summitcommunications.net,ibrahim.sharif@summitcommunications.net,ishtiak.mahmud@summitcommunications.net,md.shariful@summitcommunications.net,sadaf.mahmud@summitcommunications.net,saeed.naser@summitcommunications.net,raihan.parvez@summitcommunications.net,ahsanur.rab@summitcommunications.net,akm.badruddoza@summitcommunications.net,farhan.solaiman@summitcommunications.net,al.mamun@summitcommunications.net,obaid.masum@summitcommunications.net,anowarul.amzad@summitcommunications.net,minhazul.islam@summitcommunications.net,fahim.shahariar@summitcommunications.net,saeed.naser@summitcommunications.net', 'followUpMeeting', 'closed', 0, 22, 'anika.sharmin', 'SLA Issue: SLA needed for OH links in implementation phase. Currently no SLA is maintained due to team shortage and work load. From NOC we are expecting 4hrs of SLA, as we have seen redundancy lost and handed over to client, it should be consider with priority.\r\nImplementation team will provide us the feedback after communicating with respective HOD.\r\n\r\n*According to  Ehsan bhai,  Implementation team has already discussed with their respective HOD for this issue and yet the decision is pending. Due to this, we have extended the deadline  till 27/07/2016 15:00.\r\n**Cross Functional Meeting between Implementation and NOC, which was going  to be held on  27/07/2016 15:00,  had been postponed due to ''Project DELA'' meeting. That''s why we extended the deadline  till 03/08/2016 15:00.\r\n*** Implementation team still didn''t get decision from their respective HOD. This issue is in decision making stage.\r\n\r\n\r\nNCR issue: In the case of emergency NCR issue,  root cause for the NCR should be provided by I&C team.\r\n* For NCR mail Implementation team will provide client concern''s information.\r\n\r\nSMS Group: NOC will give sms to implementation team for each implementation issues. For this Implementation will share sms group members contact details.\r\n\r\nDash board Update: Dashboard updating should  be taken care. Training session is done. Implementation (OH) team is observing NOC tool.\r\nI&C filtering issue at dash board has been solved.\r\n\r\nHandover Information: NOC demands handover information of links in weekly basis. Implementation team will provide decision  within next meeting. \r\nIt will be better if Implementation store handover information in common folder.\r\n\r\nMeeting schedule: It is decided that from next meeting,  the meeting will be held by weekly basis. So our next meeting will be on 17th August, 2016.', ',saeed.naser,minhazul.islam,anika.sharmin,raihan.parvez,razib.hasan,obaid.masum,ibrahim.sharif,ahsanur.rab', 'anika.sharmin[2016/08/03 12:27:56] : ', '', 'NOC', 'NOC,Implementation,Implementation', 'Weekly'),
