(10, 8, 'IOS Performance ', 'rakibur.rahman@summitcommunications.net', '2016-07-17 15:00:00', '2016-07-21 15:00:00', 'closed', 'The Performance towards Malaysia is decreasing specially in busy hours through GVTL. Routing also been modified after observing the performance. Communicated with GVTL(mail & verbally) several times regarding this issue. Performance much improved now a days. whenever the performance decreases we route the traffic accordingly. Also monitoring the malaysia performance closely through GVTL. When the performance decreased we changed the routing accordingly GVTL', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '80-100', 10),
(11, 8, 'Crossfuctional Meeting with other department', 'hadeatul.islam@summitcommunications.net', '2016-07-17 15:00:00', '2016-07-24 15:00:00', 'closed', 'We are attending regular cross function meeting', '2016-07-24 16:10:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '80-100', 11),
(12, 8, 'Roaming route for Banglalink', 'hadeatul.islam@summitcommunications.net,rakibur.rahman@summitcommunications.net', '2016-07-17 15:00:00', '2016-07-19 17:00:00', 'closed', 'We have already communicated with BL for integrating roaming route. BL want to integrate the roaming route by 19th july office hours. Due to issues at BL end the scheduled work completed on 20th july. Necessary call test also done successfully. BL want to push traffic from 21st July on test basis. BL already started pumping roaming traffic through Summit-ICX from 21st july.', '2016-07-21 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '80-100', 12),
(13, 8, 'BTCL connectivity', 'hadeatul.islam@summitcommunications.net', '2016-07-17 15:00:00', '2016-10-31 15:00:00', 'closed', 'Agreement and necessary document from our side has already been submitted to Corporate Affairs. CA submitted the document to Commercial Department of BTCL for agreement singing. The commercial deformation is not yet been decided.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-08-31 04:10:06', '80-100', 13),
(14, 8, 'IPTSP connectivity', 'hadeatul.islam@summitcommunications.net', '2016-07-17 15:00:00', '2016-07-24 15:00:00', 'closed', 'Corporate Affairs will not concern about IPTSP connectivity. They suggested us to involve with marketing Department regarding new IPTSP connectivity. We have already started visiting to selected IPTSP clients with marketing concerns and expecting more co-operation from marketing concerns regarding this.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '80-100', 14),
(15, 8, 'New STM for GP(Dhaka Region)', 'shoeb.shahriar@summitcommunications.net', '2016-07-17 15:00:00', '2016-07-20 17:00:00', 'closed', 'GP will provide STM plan on 2nd August 2016', '2016-07-21 11:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '80-100', 15),
