(19, 8, 'Toolbox for ICX', 'rakibur.rahman@summitcommunications.net', '2016-07-17 15:00:00', '2016-08-01 19:00:00', 'closed', 'Shoeb bhai will consult this issue with Ilmul bhai by 21st July''16. After getting confirmation from Shoeb bhai a PR will be submitted. Shoeb bhai confirmed to give PR. PR will be sent by 21st July.PR is ready. Waiting for Ilmul bhai''s sign. Already discussed with Ilmul bhai regarding PR. We will observe proper utilization of Power meter & Laser pointer for next few days. Then we will again inform Ilmul bhai regarding this issue.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '80-100', 19),
