(30, 18, 'Dhaka region ROBI & GP third path  ', 'ronjue.ahmed@summitcommunications.net,rabeya.anzum@summitcommunications.net', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'active', 'The required activities for third path configuration are: 1. Configuration of flood group for ISIS will be done. For this required Junos version will be shared by juniper 2. Flood group will be configured at test bed(responsibel:PAD & juniper) 3. after successful floodgroup testing we will start adding third path  (responsible: PAD & juniper). 4. juniper will verify the third path configuration testing and based on juniper configuration we will deploy our network.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0-50', 46),
